					Latest Key Developments (Source: Significant Developments)




Eckoh PLC announces five-year contract secured by PSS
Tuesday, 24 Nov 2015 02:00am EST 
Eckoh PLC:Says that its recently acquired subsidiary Product Support Solutions Inc (PSS) has been selected by a major global communications company (the client) to provide an Agent Desktop solution for its contact centre operations in the USA. 
			
Full Article





Eckoh PLC secure payments contract
Wednesday, 11 Nov 2015 02:00am EST 
Eckoh PLC:Says it has secured a new three-year contract to provide secure payment services to one of the multi-media retailers, broadcasting to over 200 million homes worldwide. 
			
Full Article





Eckoh PLC says Wins Three Year Secure Payments Contract with The Co-operative Group
Wednesday, 23 Sep 2015 02:01am EDT 
Eckoh PLC:Says it has secured a new contract for its secure payment solution CallGuard with The Co-operative Group following a competitive tender.Says The three year deal will see CallGuard implemented throughout The Co-operative Group's contact centres in its Electrical, Legal Services, Group Finance and FuneralCare divisions.Says These divisions take in excess of 250,000 calls per year through approximately 125 customer service representatives. 
			
Full Article





Eckoh PLC announces dividend update
Wednesday, 19 Aug 2015 02:00am EDT 
Eckoh PLC:Confirms that further to its full year results announcement of June 25, the board proposes that dividend of 0.37 pence per share to be proposed at the company's AGM in Sept. will be payable on Oct. 30, to shareholders on the register at Oct. 2. 
			
Full Article





Eckoh PLC secures Payment contract
Monday, 17 Aug 2015 02:00am EDT 
Eckoh PLC:Announces a number of new contract wins for its secure payments products signed since the start of the new financial year.Says these international contracts have been signed respectively with an airline operator in South Africa, a consultancy organisation in Morocco and a public sector organisation in Canada. 
			
Full Article





