The Future of Customer Service



          觀看次數：4,731
        

            4 年前
          



          Consumers are becoming more self-sufficient. Subsequently, Customer Services departments are introducing more ways for their customers to self-help when making orders and purchases. These include automated call options (using menus); voice recognition systems; email responses; and web forms for feedback and/or complaints. Agents are now being viewed as trusted advisers and are increasingly being contacted for complex enquiries. Combining all these elements to create a seamless, multi-channel customer experience is the challenge businesses are now facing. Eckoh provides a full range of customer self service solutions that can help achieve this objective. Contact us to find out more: www.eckoh.com
          
顯示節錄內容
          


閱讀詳情
        
















