Sale of Ordinary Shares by Eckoh EBT

30th June 2017
Eckoh announces that on both 12 June 2017 and 22 June 2017 Eckoh’s employee benefit trust (“EBT”), sold 3,028 ordinary shares in the capital of the Company (the “Shares”). 
